📣 NEW FIBER TUBE XL LASER : FEATURE
3D CONTOUR BEVEL HEAD

The TUBE XL bevel cutting head is meticulously engineered to handle multi-axis movement, which means it can pivot and rotate in multiple directions. This capability makes it exceptionally well-suited for executing complex cuts on a variety of profiles, including round, square, and rectangular shapes. The slim profile of the cutting head is a significant advantage, as it allows the tool to access and work on profiles that were previously deemed unreachable or too challenging to cut with traditional methods. This innovation opens up new possibilities for intricate designs and enhances the efficiency and quality of the cutting process.

Post du fil d’actualité numéro 18

MachitechMachitech 4 223 abonnés4 223 abonnés 3 sem. • Il y a 3 semaines
📣 NEW FIBER TUBE XL LASER : FEATURE
TRIPLE CHUCK SYSTEM - ZERO TAIL CUTTING

The innovative 3-chuck design of the NEW FIBER TUBE XL LASER offers unparalleled stability and precision. By effectively minimizing vibration, this design ensures that each cut is executed with exacting accuracy, thereby preventing any misalignment that could compromise the quality of the final product. This precision is particularly beneficial in high-speed, high-accuracy industrial tube cutting applications, where even the slightest deviation can lead to significant material waste and increased production costs. Furthermore, the 3-chuck system facilitates zero tail cutting, a feature that allows for the complete utilization of the material being processed. This means that the end of the tube, which is often discarded as waste in traditional cutting methods, is now fully utilized, resulting in close to no material waste.

To discover more, check out our website. ⬇️
 https://hubs.ly/Q039Pmrr0

DYNAMIC PIERCE PUNCH TECHNOLOGY

Machitech’s Dynamic Punch Pierce technology minimizes thick plate cratering and protects optics by optimizing focus, gas flow, power, and frequency. This advanced approach enables some of the fastest pierce times in the industry.

It's time to upgrade your HPR400XD for the new Hypertherm XPR460 : the industry new gold standard for high-thickness plasma cutting!

✔️ Versatility: Capable of cutting different materials and thicknesses, making it suitable for a wide range of applications.

✔️ Precision: It provides superior part-to-part consistency, ensuring high-quality cuts with minimized dross, which helps reduce the need for secondary operations.

✔️ Durability of Consumables: The longer consumable life contributes to lower operating costs by maintaining performance across extensive use.

Stronger than ever, focused on the future

We are proud to announce our new branding initiative, marking an exciting new chapter in our evolution. As part of this initiative, Machitech has merged its two specialized divisions, Alpha Lazer and Beamcut, into a unified entity under the Machitech brand. This strategic move is designed to enhance our offerings and reinforce our commitment to providing cutting-edge solutions to customers, coupled with the best service the industry has to offer.
Our new branding evolution reflects Machitech’s growth and transformation, positioning our company for continued success in an ever-changing marketplace and symbolizes our commitment to innovation, quality, and customer-centric solutions.

All updates and news from Beamcut and Alpha Lazer will now be shared directly on the Machitech page.

Post du fil d’actualité numéro 120

MachitechMachitech 4 223 abonnés4 223 abonnés 11 mois • Il y a 1 an
🎉 INCROYABLE DONATION 🎉
Nous sommes fiers d'annoncer que Machitech a récemment remis un don record de plus de 65 000 $ à Sclérose en Plaques Canada - Capitale-Nationale ! 💙 En 2023, plus de 230 membres dévoués de notre équipe, ainsi que nos partenaires et fournisseurs, se sont mobilisés pour soutenir cette cause vitale.

La sclérose en plaques est une maladie auto-immune chronique qui affecte le système nerveux central, y compris le cerveau, la moelle épinière et les nerfs optiques. Les symptômes peuvent varier, allant de troubles de la vision à des problèmes de mémoire, d'équilibre et de mobilité. Rejoignez-nous dans notre engagement envers SP Canada et découvrez comment vous pouvez aider sur www.spcanada.ca.

🎉 INCREDIBLE DONATION 🎉
We are proud to announce that Machitech has recently made a record donation of over $65,000 to SP Canada - Capital-National! 💙 In 2023, more than 230 dedicated members of our team, along with our partners and suppliers, rallied to support this vital cause.

Multiple sclerosis is a chronic autoimmune disease that affects the central nervous system, including the brain, spinal cord, and optic nerves. Symptoms can vary, ranging from vision problems to issues with memory, balance, and mobility. Join us in our commitment to SP Canada and find out how you can help at www.spcanada.ca.
